{"tid":640173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭:中國從無將香港主權交給第三者","createTime":"2018-04-24T05:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T07:58:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":137,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"6cdf5f6b68d99c955d24b15014dee527907e0e03","tid":640173,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:50:07.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥表示，教科書評審委員會要求高中歷史教科書用字更精準無可厚非，外界不應以有色眼鏡去看。<br />\n<br />\n高中歷史科教科書的評審準則近日引起爭議。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥指委員會要求教科書用字更精準，無可厚非，外界不應過份敏感。<br />\n<br />\n她指，其中一個例子形容中國收回香港主權，而中國從來沒有將香港主權交給第三者，所以在基本法的引言「中華人民共和國是恢復行使在香港的主權」，這個是更加精準的說法。<br />\n<br />\n被問主張「結束一黨專政」是否能夠參選，林鄭月娥表示，中聯辦主任王志民比她熟悉憲法，已將有關概念解釋清楚，她很難作出任何保證。<br />\n<br />\n另外，前全國人大法律委員會主任委員喬曉陽提出反對國家實行社會主義是違憲。林鄭月娥表示中央一直堅守一國兩制，讓香港實行資本主義，港人亦應尊重內地制度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BE%9E%E7%84%A1%E5%B0%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E4%BA%A4%E7%B5%A6%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E8%80%85-041410174.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BE%259E%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25AC%258A%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%2580%2585-041410174.html&d=vHuKfvF7bamx%2B%2BckcQho87IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c72fe0e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BE%9E%E7%84%A1%E5%B0%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E4%BA%A4%E7%B5%A6%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E8%80%85-041410174.html</a>"},{"pid":"18f0950e6beefcc5e04824c5631e057b75055946","tid":640173,"uid":12021,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:51:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"911ef2d849aea6eaec665209f80468b400af4de8","tid":640173,"uid":48083,"like":118,"dislike":2,"score":116,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:52:40.000Z","msg":"即係以下機構/人仕唔精準啦<br />\n<br />\n中國人民政治協商會議全國委員會(全國政協):<br />\n<br />\n(一國兩制)即&ldquo;一個國家，兩種制度&rdquo;的簡稱。中國共產黨和中國政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為了收回香港、澳門主權</span></strong></span>，實現台灣與祖國大陸統一而提出的一項重要戰略方針。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cppcc.gov.cn/2011/09/26/ARTI1317001118812175.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cppcc.gov.cn%2F2011%2F09%2F26%2FARTI1317001118812175.shtml&d=vHuKfvF7bamx%2B%2BckcQho87IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d0aed6eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cppcc.gov.cn/2011/09/26/ARTI1317001118812175.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n1983年國務院政府工作報告<br />\n...我們還將在適當的時候<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>收回香港主權</strong></span></span>，並且採取適當措施維持香港繁榮。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gov.cn/test/2006-02/16/content_200823.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Ftest%2F2006-02%2F16%2Fcontent_200823.htm&d=vHuKfvF7bamx%2B%2BckcQho87IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0851655b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gov.cn/test/2006-02/16/content_200823.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中國幹部學習網:<br />\n自從香港淪陷並被割讓以來，祖國人民眷念香港同胞，從未放棄過<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>收回香港主權</strong></span></span>的努力。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ccln.gov.cn/xxzgyc/253653-1.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccln.gov.cn%2Fxxzgyc%2F253653-1.shtml&d=vHuKfvF7bamx%2B%2BckcQho87IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=703a4c6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ccln.gov.cn/xxzgyc/253653-1.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n中國國防部<br />\n&ldquo;一國&rdquo;體現了中國要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>收回香港主權</strong></span></span>的堅定決心，&ldquo;兩制&rdquo;則充分考慮了香港歷史的特殊性，充分調動了香港民眾的積極性，&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;的成功有其必然性。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mod.gov.cn/big5/jmsd/2017-07/01/content_4784333.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mod.gov.cn%2Fbig5%2Fjmsd%2F2017-07%2F01%2Fcontent_4784333.htm&d=vHuKfvF7bamx%2B%2BckcQho87IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=eb4c21dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mod.gov.cn/big5/jmsd/2017-07/01/content_4784333.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n在後來出版的《鄧小平》文選中，清晰記錄下了這次談話的內容，&ldquo;我先把中央已決定的原則與大家講一講，到1997年必須<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收回香港主權</span></strong></span>，這是原則問題，不可討論的，但對香港仍要繼續維持自由港，貿易金融中心不變，即根據憲法草案第三十條原對台灣的也可用之香港，使其繼續留在資本主義制度。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://phtv.ifeng.com/a/20170627/44643763_0.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphtv.ifeng.com%2Fa%2F20170627%2F44643763_0.shtml&d=vHuKfvF7bamx%2B%2BckcQho87IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=887b4c96\" target=\"_blank\">http://phtv.ifeng.com/a/20170627/44643763_0.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"6e691fedb4d81b328d77936fef8f51e2d26207d7","tid":640173,"uid":163350,"like":79,"dislike":2,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:52:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4e3b0a5d75f3c2a0635221bba47c31013b277db","tid":640173,"uid":143597,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:52:59.000Z","msg":"結束一人專政"},{"pid":"aed11fcb6fcc3aec65a40747d4e04c13ccf33121","tid":640173,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"岩呀，好撚屈辱咁俾人夾硬租左呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95304dd6da445fd9cb58661d712126710dfec6a9","tid":640173,"uid":49588,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"香港島是永久割讓給大英祖國！"},{"pid":"f9b62ffe98ef9a8f07b53abf394fd25f50316c55","tid":640173,"uid":42435,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:01:21.000Z","msg":"請問林鄭奶媽97 前邊個國家政府出糧比你?"},{"pid":"e56ca43a1fa2396bc538d7d6ce5f0c3d9738030a","tid":640173,"uid":48234,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:03:41.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國係<span style=\"color: gold;\">奪取</span>香港主權唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">收回</span>呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb15903d1731401819f8f77ab914d3d1bf3aa5f4","tid":640173,"uid":36857,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"都無主權，何來收回?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n南京條約正本仲喺中華民國手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b095c4aa0689940b4b0465e88b1b36c90ac2de48","tid":640173,"uid":142888,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:06:54.000Z","msg":"應該直接問佢係唔係否定港英政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到咁含蓄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94479c329cb8e065ec991b0b8e96f71a72280fe0","tid":640173,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:06:57.000Z","msg":"滿清政府從無喪權辱國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d616e7a4822f39cb3724c4546ffc5397d615b3","tid":640173,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"中国又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fc9b30082daf6a9efd8494d91d337d914b059e","tid":640173,"uid":59695,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"林鄭意思係鄧小平當年配合英國人鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6baa1aa11ac7a5a8884d15f803d53757d558195e","tid":640173,"uid":23180,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"教科書教歷史唔叫人reference睇番條文，仲叫人唔好小題大做，本身個心地已經差<br />\n<br />\n日日吹法治法治，法你老母治咩<br />\n<br />\n抵你嫁著個垃圾老公嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3c7ffec938ad4aa586f9724744ab0d123bc2cb","tid":640173,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:13:15.000Z","msg":"跟本就未夾掂口供<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56afbbe84c301ceac1e99cac79f167dcfbadb4b2","tid":640173,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c3c7ffec938ad4aa586f9724744ab0d123bc2cb","tid":640173,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:13:15.000Z","msg":"跟本就未夾掂口供<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"根"},{"pid":"843739d2b9b0a590abe8db199c66ffe4c0ab44b8","tid":640173,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打敗仗割地賠償同將主權交比人有咩分別"},{"pid":"494cb729df75cac5916aeb81268876d1afd9a237","tid":640173,"uid":93784,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:16:02.000Z","msg":"認同用字係要精準<br />\n<br />\n但楊x雄個版本連精準都唔係 <br />\n<br />\n收回呢兩隻字 語意上本身有問題都算<br />\n<br />\n而家話無將香港主權交比第三者 講法係違反歷史事實<br />\n<br />\n佢地為左防止人聯想起英治時期香港曾經「獨立」於中國以外 <br />\n<br />\n又指香港在中國南方 又怕人諗起港獨 <br />\n<br />\n最敏感就係呢班狗官 仲話外界敏感 屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c46b39a5b15166fbaf1547d6dd2671cf1a403b4","tid":640173,"uid":34755,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"咁佢姐係話鄧小平唔岩啦，快d落去同佢對質啦"},{"pid":"2fff4b766d26259687e9a53484875a9adeb98503","tid":640173,"uid":66496,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:16:49.000Z","msg":"咁易又分心 <br />\n講返人工島先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64abe64a416304e5a31e1974c5d8add6ed75672","tid":640173,"uid":41928,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:18:45.000Z","msg":"南